node.text:
💁🏻‍♂️Whether you’re spending the weekend working, relaxing, or celebrating (we’re doing all of the above), here’s a fun #vacationhome that’s a total escape!! 🙆🏻‍♂️ Swipe for the full tour... ☝🏻FYI the first shot is a freshwater pond, but the rest are #oceanview!
.
🙏🏻Also, after a week of kind of sweltering weather, the perfect weather has come out like clockwork, and we’ve got temps in the 70s and 80s for the weekend 🤗 happy #fourthofjuly to you!
.
🙋🏻‍♂️Coming to you with some coffee and beautiful #homedesign by @caldwellandjohnson from our #boathouse this morning. Stay cool and safe… and have fun! #watchhillrhodeisland
